org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web

Class WebCloudlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.Cloudlet
      • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.plus.disk.HddCloudlet
        • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web.WebCloudlet

  • public class WebCloudlet
extends HddCloudlet
    A web cloudlet is a cloudlet, which is a part of a web session. Usually it is small in terms of RAM and CPU. Each web cloudlet is contained within a web session.
    A distinct property of a web cloudlet is that it has ideal start time. This ideal start time can be met, but can also be postponed if the previous web cloudlets in the web session are delayed. Thus there is a difference between the ideal start time and the actual start time.
    Author:
    nikolay.grozev
